{"id":4,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":4,"title":"Matthew 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The wise men are directed by a star to Jesus—Joseph takes the child to Egypt—Herod slays the children in Bethlehem—Jesus is taken to Nazareth to dwell."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.1","order":"03.03.002.110"},["b","1"],"Now when Jesus was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"born"],"in Bethlehem of Judæa in the days of Herod the king, behold, there came wise men from the east to Jerusalem,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.2","order":"03.03.002.111"},["b","2"],"Saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Where"],"is he that is born",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"King of the Jews"],"? for we have seen his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"star"],"in the east, and are come to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"worship"],"him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.3","order":"03.03.002.112"},["b","3"],"When Herod the king had heard",["i","these things,"],"he was troubled, and all Jerusalem with him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.4","order":"03.03.002.113"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"And"],"when he had gathered all the chief priests and scribes of the people together, he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"demanded"],"of them where Christ should be born."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.5","order":"03.03.002.114"},["b","5"],"And they said unto him, In Bethlehem of Judæa: for thus it is written by the prophet,"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.6","order":"03.03.002.115"},["b","6"],"And thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Bethlehem"],",",["i","in"],"the land of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"Juda"],", art not the least among the princes of Juda: for out of thee shall come a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"Governor"],", that shall",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"rule"],"my people Israel."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.7","order":"03.03.002.116"},["b","7"],"Then Herod, when he had privily called the wise men, inquired of them diligently what time the star appeared."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.8","order":"03.03.002.117"},["b","8"],"And he sent them to Bethlehem, and said, Go and search diligently for the young child; and when ye have found",["i","him,"],"bring me word again, that I may come and worship him also."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.9","order":"03.03.002.118"},["b","9"],"When they had heard the king, they departed; and, lo, the star, which they saw in the east, went before them, till it came and stood over where the young child was."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.10","order":"03.03.002.119"},["b","10"],"When they saw the star, they rejoiced with exceeding great joy."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.11","order":"03.03.002.120"},["b","11"],"¶And when they were come into the house, they saw the young child with Mary his mother, and fell down, and worshipped him: and when they had opened their treasures, they presented unto him gifts; gold, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"frankincense"],", and myrrh."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.12","order":"03.03.002.121"},["b","12"],"And being warned of God in a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"dream"],"that they should not return to Herod, they departed into their own country another way."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.13","order":"03.03.002.122"},["b","13"],"And when they were departed, behold, the angel of the Lord appeareth to Joseph in a dream, saying, Arise, and take the young child and his mother, and flee into Egypt, and be thou there until I bring thee word: for Herod will seek the young child to destroy him."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.14","order":"03.03.002.123"},["b","14"],"When he arose, he took the young child and his mother by night, and departed into Egypt:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.15","order":"03.03.002.124"},["b","15"],"And was there until the death of Herod: that it might be fulfilled which was spoken of the Lord by the prophet, saying, Out of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Egypt"],"have I called my son."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.16","order":"03.03.002.125"},["b","16"],"¶Then Herod, when he saw that he was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"mocked of"],"the wise men,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"was exceeding wroth"],", and sent forth, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"slew"],"all the children that were in Bethlehem, and in all the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_16d"},"coasts"],"thereof, from two years old and under, according to the time which he had diligently inquired of the wise men."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.17","order":"03.03.002.126"},["b","17"],"Then was fulfilled that which was spoken by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Jeremy"],"the prophet, saying,"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.18","order":"03.03.002.127"},["b","18"],"In",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Rama"],"was there a voice heard, lamentation, and weeping, and great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"mourning"],", Rachel weeping",["i","for"],"her",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"children"],", and would not be comforted, because they are not."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.19","order":"03.03.002.128"},["b","19"],"¶But when Herod was dead, behold, an angel of the Lord appeareth in a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"dream"],"to Joseph in Egypt,"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.20","order":"03.03.002.129"},["b","20"],"Saying, Arise, and take the young child and his mother, and go into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"land of Israel"],": for they are dead which sought the young child’s life."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.21","order":"03.03.002.130"},["b","21"],"And he arose, and took the young child and his mother, and came into the land of Israel."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.22","order":"03.03.002.131"},["b","22"],"But when he heard that Archelaus did reign in Judæa in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"room"],"of his father Herod, he was afraid to go thither: notwithstanding, being warned of God in a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"dream"],", he turned aside into the parts of Galilee:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.23","order":"03.03.002.132"},["b","23"],"And he came and dwelt in a city called",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"Nazareth"],": that it might be fulfilled which was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"spoken"],"by the prophets, He shall be called a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"Nazarene"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.1a","order":"03.03.002.133"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-birth-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Birth of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.2a","order":"03.03.002.135"},["b","2a"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 3:2 … Where is",["i","the child"],"that is born,",["i","the Messiah"],"of the Jews? …"],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.2b","order":"03.03.002.137"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/6.5"},"Isa. 6:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/23.5"},"Jer. 23:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.14"},"2 Ne. 10:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.50"},"Alma 5:50"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.22.22-23"},"D&C 128:22 (22–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.53"},"Moses 7:53"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.2c","order":"03.03.002.139"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptu